OL,3,CRAF Chinook crash families apply for
OL,4,Cjudicial review over public inquiry
OL,5,Crefusal
OL,7,FFamilies of those killed in the RAF
OL,8,FChinook crash have formally applied
OL,9,Ffor a judicial review into the
OL,10,Fgovernment's refusal to hold a public
OL,11,Finquiry into the disaster.
OL,13,F29 senior security personnel were
OL,14,Fkilled when the helicopter crashed on
OL,15,Fthe Mull of Kintyre during a flight
OL,16,Ffrom Northern Ireland to Scotland in
OL,17,F1994.
OL,19,FIt has been claimed the aircraft was
OL,20,Fon a "show flight" to prove its
OL,21,Fairworthiness.
