OL,7,FHowever, the Ministry of Defence has
OL,8,Fpreviously said it has no information
OL,9,Fto support such a theory.
OL,11,FOn Friday, Alliance MP Sorcha Eastwood
OL,12,Falongside Labour MP Ian Byrne brought
OL,13,Fa motion to the Commons calling for a
OL,14,Fjudge-led probe into the crash to
OL,15,Fensure accountability and justice for
OL,16,Fthose whose lives were lost.
OL,18,FThe incident was initially blamed on
OL,19,Fpilot error before this was overturned
OL,20,Fin 2011.
